    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Patri et Filii et Spiritus Sancti. Anno Deo propitio pontificatus
                        domini nostri <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/2410">Benedicti</persName>
                        summi <rs key="#Popes">pontifici</rs> et universali papae in apostolica
                        sacratissima beati Petri hapostoli Domini sede anno tertio atque imperante
                        domino piissimo perpetuo haugustus <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/239">Ottone</persName> ha Deo coronato pacifico magno <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperatore</rs> in Italia vero anno sextodecimo, die
                        septimo mensis ... indictione undecima, <placeName ref="#places/594"
                            >Ravennae</placeName>. Etenim quae gesta esse videntur prolixis
                        temporibus memoriter retineri non possumus, ideo scripture vinculis anotari
                        ... cum Christi auxilium dum adessem ego quidem <persName
                            key="#Tabellio #Consules" ref="#people/1555">Iohannis</persName> Dei
                        nutu ex genere <rs key="#Consules">consulis</rs> et <rs key="#Tabellio"
                            >tabellio</rs> huius civitatis Ravennae, in <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                        ...fivit... ibique mecum pariter bonissimis atque <rs key="#Vir_inluster"
                            >illustrissimis viris</rs> et bonae hobinionis atque laudabilis famae
                        viris corum nomina haec sunt, idest: <persName key="#Vir_inluster"><name
                                ref="Petrus de Traversaria">Petrus qui vocatur de
                            Traversaria</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke #Vir_inluster"><name ref="Paulus de Traversaria"
                                >Paulus <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> de
                            Traversaria</name></persName>, <persName key="#Vir_inluster #Consules"
                            ref="#people/92"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Consules">consul(e)</rs> et pater civitatis, <persName
                            key="#Vir_inluster"><name ref="Paulus">Paulus</name></persName> qui
                        vocatur ... <persName><name ref="Egilo">Egila</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Rodualdus">Rodaldus</name></persName> filio
                                <persName><name ref="Rodualdus">Rodaldus</name></persName> magister
                        militum, <persName key="#Consules"><name ref="Leo/Liutio de Anestaliolo"
                                >Leo</name>
                            <rs key="#Consules">consule</rs> qui vocatur Liutio de
                            Anestaliolo</persName>, <persName><name ref="Paulus de Gandilo"
                                >Paulus</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Andreas de Gandilo">Andreas</name></persName> germani de
                        Gandilo, <persName><name ref="Petrus de Antio">Petrus de
                            Antio</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Atto"
                            >Atio</name></persName> filio suo, <persName><name ref="Richardus"
                                >Richardo</name></persName> fil(io) quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Benotus">Benotus</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Martinus de Magno">Martinus de Magno</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#vassusOf"><name ref="Everardus"
                            >Verardo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Consules"><name
                                ref="Romanus">Romanus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Consules">consul(e)</rs> et <persName><name ref="Paulus"
                                >Paulo</name></persName> filio suo, <persName key="#Chancellor"
                                ><name ref="Bernardus">Bernardo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellario</rs> et aliis plures qui longum est
                        atscribendum; in nostri et homnium presentiam haccedens dominus predictus
                        Everardus <rs key="#vassusOf">vassus</rs>
                        <rs key="#dominus/seniorOf">dominus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Marquis/duke #Palatine_count #dominus/seniorOf"><name
                                ref="Anselmus">Anselmus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchio</rs> et <rs key="#Palatine_count">comes
                            palatii</rs> domni Ottonis imperatoris, pariter cum <persName
                            key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Bernardus">Bernardo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> et adpreenderunt cantum muri de <rs
                            key="#Houses">mansione pedeplana</rs> in interius ... ac civitate
                        Ravennae, in regione ... et misit in manum domini <persName key="#Consules"
                                ><name ref="Romanus/Romizo">Romanus</name>
                            <rs key="#Consules">cons(ulis)</rs> qui vocatur Romizo</persName> et in
                        manum <persName><name ref="Bonizo">Bonizo</name></persName> filio
                                <persName><name ref="Petronio">Petronio</name></persName> seo et
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petro</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Petronia">Petronia</name></persName> germana et
                        Romanus consul qui vocatur Romizo declaravit et dixerunt: ‘Ecce investimus
                        vobis de omnes pertinetias in integrum de ista mansione qui fuit de quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Paulus/de Romano">Paulus qui vocabatur de
                                Romano</name></persName> et ge... pertinentias vestras de locum qui
                        vocatur <placeName key="#Plebs">Manova</placeName>, situs territorio
                            <placeName ref="#places/3512" key="#Fines"><geogName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#estates/2409">Corneliense</geogName></placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Plebs">plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs">Sancti Petri in Brusio</orgName>, salva querela; unde
                        reclamastis per tres vicibus in placitis domini Anselmi marchionis et
                        comitis palatio domini Ottonis imperatoris'. Et ipse Romanus consul(e) qui
                        vocatur Romizo pariter cum Bonizo nepoti suo seo et a Petro et a Petronia
                        germana sicut dixerunt: '...nos eam sic recepimus et deprecamur vos homnes
                        pro futurum testimonium'. Hoc si … hec … dan … um et diem et mense et
                        indictione ut s(upra) undecima, Ravenna...</ab>
